						               													<description>A game specifically designed for young wargamers! It is just a 4 page book.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Incorporating three levels of play, Mein Panzer Junior can be played by children as young as 5 years old, or upwards of 12 years old or more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Level One introduces youngsters to the basic fundamentals of wargaming, using only a single d6 per player and a common 6&amp;quot;  or 12&amp;quot; ruler. Resolution of movement and shooting is simple  and easily accomplished by the youngest players on a tank by tank basis.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Level Two expands upon the previous level slightly by adding  Tank  Units and the concept of &amp;ldquo;hits&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;kills&amp;rdquo;. Play is still extremely simple with only a few additional rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Level Three is almost a full featured game including game turns and distinction between the different types of tanks.  At this level, players must be able to perform simple subtraction relatively quickly to maintain a smooth, and interesting, game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
